Package com.idevicesinc.sweetblue

Interface HistoricalDataLoadListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericListener_Void<HistoricalDataLoadListener.HistoricalDataLoadEvent>
    public interface HistoricalDataLoadListener
extends GenericListener_Void<HistoricalDataLoadListener.HistoricalDataLoadEvent>
    A callback that is used by various overloads of BleDevice.loadHistoricalData() that accept instances hereof. You can also set default listeners on BleDevice.setListener_HistoricalDataLoad(HistoricalDataLoadListener) and BleManager.setListener_HistoricalDataLoad(HistoricalDataLoadListener). The GenericListener_Void.onEvent(Event) method is called when the historical data for a given characteristic UUID is done loading from disk.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static class  HistoricalDataLoadListener.HistoricalDataLoadEvent
      Event struct passed to GenericListener_Void.onEvent(Event) that provides further information about the status of a historical data load to memory using BleDevice.loadHistoricalData() (or overloads).
      static class  HistoricalDataLoadListener.Status
      Enumerates the status codes for operations kicked off from BleDevice.loadHistoricalData() (or overloads).
